TopicTitle: *Old Memories* Do you remember your first rocket to the Mun. I do the Delta IV (Highly original)

Articles.Content:
We all have our stories of landing on Gilly, Moho, Eeloo but I wanted to show you guys my Delta IV (Yes derived from that rocket that isn't made for the Mun). Anyways, I wanted to show & tell my story way-y-y-yy back then when I was a big noob. So I found the craft and took it for a flight.

Javascript is disabled. View full album

So now after seeing my successful launch that I with only 20 monopropellant left in the tank, show & tell your adventure to the Mun. Im sure it will be great to hear.

You can choose to download this craft if you want it to @ https://www.dropbox.com/s/dpnnipir0f4pua8/Delta%20IV%20Heavy%20Manned%20V3.craft?dl=0

Mini-challenge: Download the Delta-iv and post a picture of how much monopropellant you have left in your tank. It will be cool to see.
